TENDL-2025 (TALYS Evaluated Nuclear Data Library)                 9040 1451   11
                                                                  9040 1451   12
Neutron general purpose library                                   9040 1451   13
                                                                  9040 1451   14
Author: A.J. Koning and D. Rochman, IAEA - PSI                    9040 1451   15
                                                                  9040 1451   16
Ref.: A.J. Koning, D. Rochman, J.-Ch. Sublet, N. Dzysiuk,         9040 1451   17
      M. Fleming, and S. van der Marck, TENDL: Complete nuclear   9040 1451   18
